quran[13]{c,v,t}:
  27,1,"(Taa Siin) hari yewtere fii yeru …óee fe∆¥∆¥iino ka cortewol Albaqara. ∆äee Aayeeje jippinaa…óe e dow maa…óa, ko …óen woni Aayeeje Alqur'aanaare nden, e Deftere …ìanngunde ko jil…ìi alaa e mayre, kala taskii…óo nde o annday pellet, kayre ko nde immorde ka Alla."
  27,2,"∆äee Aayeeje, ko fewnay…óe faade e Goonga kan, ko …óe wewlinay…óe gom…óin…ìe …ìen Alla e Nulaa…óo Makko on."
  27,3,"∆Åen …ìe no totta Julde nden no …ìuri timmirde, …ìe jonnira Jakka jawle ma…ì…ìe ndin na…ìirgol …óe ka …óe haani yaarude ton, hara kam…ìe ko …ìe yananaa…ìe ko woni kon ka Laakara immorde e Mbarjaari e Lepte."
  27,4,"Pellet, …ìen heeferaa…ìe …ìe gom…óinaali Laakara on e ko woni kon ton immorde e Mbarjaari e Lepte, labinanaama …ìe golle ma…ì…ìe bon…óe …óen, …ìe duu- mii e gollugol …óe, hara kam…ìe ko …ìe wemmbii…ìe …ìe yi'ataa ko hewtinta …ìe e peewal ngal."
  27,5,"∆Åen sifaa…ìe koo ko ja≈ãtaa, ko …ìen woni …ìe wooda- ni …óum lepte bon…óe ka aduna sabu wareede e daheede, kam…ìe kadi ka Laakara …ìe …ìuroyay yim…ìe …ìen fow hayrere, nokku ka …ìe hayroyta wonkiiji ma…ì…ìe e …ìeynguureeji ma…ì…ìe …óin √ëalnde Darngal sabu luttineede ma…ì…ìe ka Yiite."
  27,6,"E pellet, an -Nulaa…óo- hi…óa lonngineede ndee Alqur'aanaare jippinaandee dow maa…óa immorde ka √ëee√±o e nder tagugol Makko e fewjugol Makko e Sari'a Makko, Anndu…óo hay e huunde suu…óanaaki Mo immorde e nafaaji jeyaa…ìe Makko …ìen."
  27,7,"Ja≈ãto -an Nulaa…óo- fewndo Muusaa maakannoo yim…ìe makko …ìen: Min dey mi yi'ii yiite, mi adda-noyay on ka nge woni …óon kumpital immorde e Hu…ì…ìu…óo nge On, O fewna en e laawol ngol, maa…óum le, mi addana on jol…ìol yiite ∆¥ettaangol e magge jortagol wonnde on iwloray nge immorde e jaangol ngol."
  27,8,"Tuma nde o yottinoo nokku ka yiite nge o hayninoo ngen woni …óon, Alla noddi mo: Ko woni, Seninaama On won…óo ka yiite, e …ìen wonu…ìe …ìan≈ãe magge immorde e Malaa'ikaa…ìe …ìen, e mawninngol Jooma winndere nden e Seninngol Mo e kala ko gasantaa Mo immorde e …óin sifaaji …ói majju…ìe …ìen sifotoo Mo."
  27,9,"Alla Daalani mo: Ko an yo Muusaa, ko woni, ko Min woni Alla On Teddu…óo Mo go…ó…óowoo foolataa, ko Mi √ëee√±o e nder Tagugol Am ngol e Hoddirgol Am ngol e Sari'a Am on."
  27,10,"Li…ìu tuggordu maa…óa ndun, Muusaa ja…ìi, nde Muusaa yi'unoo ndu hindu waylitoo dilla a wi'ayma kayru ko ndu mboddi, o hucciti fii dogugol ndu o ruttaaki. Alla Daalani mo: Wata a hulu ndu, Min Nulaa…ìe …ìen hulataa ka Am mboddi wanaa tanaa mboddi kadi."
  27,11,"Kono, mo too√±irii wonkii muu…óum wa…ó…óitagol junuubu, refti o tuubi …ìaawo …óum, haray Min ko Mi Surroowo mo, Yurmetee…óo mo."
  27,12,"Naadu junngo maa…óa ngon ka wuddere dolloke maa…óa hikkiinde e ndaande nden, ngo yaltay …ìaawo ko naadu…óaa ngo kon hara hingo rawniri wa gilaasi ko aldaa e col…óo, …óum ko tawaa…óum e Aayeeje jeenay seedotoo…óe goongugol maa…óa …óen tawdaa e junngo ngon: Ko tuggordu ndun, e kokke …óen, e uytagol dim…óe …óen, e waame …óen, e kanuuji …óin, e mbu…óuuji …óin, e totiiji …óin, e ∆¥ii∆¥am …óam- faade e Fir'awna e yim…ìe makko …ìen, pellet, kam…ìe …ìe wonii yim…ìe yaltir…ìe e doftaare Alla sabu yeddugol Mo."
  27,13,"Tuma nde …óee Aayeeje Amen arunoo e ma…ì…ìe, …óen …óe Men semmbiniri …óum Muusaa ko …óe …ìanngu…óe fee√±u…óe, …ìe wi'i: Ndee huunde nde Muusaa ardi e muu…óum immorde e Aayeeje ko mbilewu …ìanngungu."